title: Coach Matt Beaman of Parrott Academy on the Free Press Football Show
text: By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III The Free Press By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III Posted Oct. 15, 2015 at 1:23 AM Updated Oct 15, 2015 at 1:46 AM By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III Posted Oct. 15, 2015 at 1:23 AM Updated Oct 15, 2015 at 1:46 AM Parrott Academy head football coach Matt Beaman joins Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III on this week's edition of the Free Press Football Show. Bryan and Junious also recap last week's games and offer their picks for this week's match ups.
